{"lemma":"صَكَّ","slug":"صَكَّ","root":"ص.ك.ك","root_slug":"ص-ك-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ك-ك","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24633"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%83%D9%8E%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"check (finances)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bond"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"deed"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bolt, to close, to shut","examples":[{"text":"صَكَّ ٱلطِّفْلُ ٱلْبَابَ","english":"The child closed the door."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to beat, to strike","examples":[{"text":"صَكَّتْ وَجْهَهُ","english":"She slapped him in his face."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Classical Persian چک (čak, “legal document, document, contract, deed of sale, bill”)."},"ipa":["/sˤakk/","/sˤak.ka/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24633","headword_ar":"صَكٌّ","root":"Sk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sak~a","text_ar":"صَكَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, * Msb, TA.)       -A2-  Also a Pers. word (S, O) arabicized, (S, Mgh, O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain writing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"called in Pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jak","text_ar":"جَك"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Jako","text_ar":"چَكْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a debenture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"written acknowledgement of a debt"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of money"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of some other thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a written statement of a commercial transaction, purchase"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sale, transfer, bargain, contract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sijil~N","text_ar":"سِجِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in this last sense or in the senses next following]: (S and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sjl","text_ar":"سجل"},{"kind":"text","text":":)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sijil~","text_ar":"سِجِلّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaADiY","text_ar":"قَاضِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sealed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"signed and sealed, statement of a judicial decision; a judicial record;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"record of a judge, in which his sentence is written"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (KL:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a written order for the payment of subsistence-money,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a stipend, salary, pension,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"allowance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which some persons used to sell, but the selling of which is forbidden: (Msb, TA:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSuk~N","text_ar":"اَصُكٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SikaAkN","text_ar":"صِكَاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SukuwkN","text_ar":"صُكُوكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, Msb, K.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapu AlS~ak~i","text_ar":"لَيْلَةُ الصَّكِّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night of the middle"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the month"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Shaa- bán;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because in it are written the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SikaAk","text_ar":"صِكَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the allowances of subsistence [of individuals]: also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapu AlbaraA='api","text_ar":"لَيْلَةُ البَرَا=ءَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, TA.) [Hence also]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sak~u","text_ar":"صَكُّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmusaAfiri","text_ar":"المُسَافِرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The traveller's pass, given him to prevent any one's offering opposition to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A and Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jwz","text_ar":"جوز"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Mgh","TA","Msb","KL"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}